(165, 1, '2016-09-13 10:54:41', '2016-09-13 10:54:41', '<div class="main-content-left">\r\n<div>Join Gloss Cartel Sydney’s latest mobile service for fast beauty delivered to the home, office, hotel, wedding &amp; event.</div>\r\n<p>\r\n<div>We are looking for hair stylists, makeup artists, nail technicians and spray tanners who are enthusiastic, flexible, self motivated and passionate about their industry. \r\n<p>\r\nYou must be impeccably presented with fantastic time management skills and have a minimum of two years experience in your chosen field.\r\n<p>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<p>\r\n<div>Gloss Cartel allows you to be your own boss, manage your own schedule, earn as much as you want when you want.</div>\r\n<p>\r\n<div>If this sounds like you, we would love to hear from you.</div></div>\r\n<p>\r\n<div>Please fill out the form and tell us a bit about yourself including your experience and we''ll get back to you soon.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class="content-bottom-contact">THE<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-470" src="http://glosscartel.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/logo-tem.png" alt="logo-tem" width="267" height="19" />team</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="main-content-right">[contact-form-7 id="150" title="Contact form"]</div>\r\n<span style="border-radius: 2px; text-indent: 20px; width: auto; padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; text-align: center; font: bold 11px/20px ''Helvetica Neue'',Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #ffffff; background: #bd081c no-repeat scroll 3px 50% / 14px 14px; position: absolute; opacity: 1; z-index: 8675309; display: none; cursor: pointer;">Save</span>', 'WE''RE HIRING', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'were-hiring', '', '', '2016-10-10 09:12:30', '2016-10-10 09:12:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost/demowp/gloss-cartel/?page_id=165', 0, 'page', '', 0),
